org.sat4j.specs
インタフェース IGroupSolver

すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
IProblem, ISolver, RandomAccessModel, java.io.Serializable
既知の実装クラスの一覧:
GroupClauseSelectorSolver, HighLevelXplain
public interface IGroupSolver
extends ISolver

Represents a CNF in which clauses are grouped into levels. It was first used to build a high level MUS solver for SAT 2011 competition.

導入されたバージョン:
2.3.3
作成者:
leberre
